01:24:20.723 --> 01:24:22.389
All right.

01:24:23.658 --> 01:24:26.060
Bless y'all.

01:24:26.062 --> 01:24:28.796
Call me if you need anything?

01:24:36.071 --> 01:24:37.571
Okay.

01:24:39.474 --> 01:24:41.341
All good.

01:24:48.817 --> 01:24:51.185
I'm sorry, dad.

01:24:54.589 --> 01:24:57.424
It's gonna be okay, sweet pea.

01:25:07.168 --> 01:25:10.604
I'm gonna miss you guys a lot.

01:25:11.706 --> 01:25:15.375
You can come visit us anytime.

01:25:16.778 --> 01:25:18.545
You, too.

01:25:24.586 --> 01:25:26.720
It's been a long time coming,

01:25:26.722 --> 01:25:31.225
but tonight, because
of what we did on this day,

01:25:31.227 --> 01:25:35.596
in this election,
at this defining moment,

01:25:35.598 --> 01:25:37.831
change has come to America!

01:25:49.310 --> 01:25:52.813
What do you ask
of this community?

01:25:52.815 --> 01:25:57.184
I ask to be
a fully incorporated member.

01:25:59.521 --> 01:26:01.855
God of mercy and compassion,

01:26:01.857 --> 01:26:05.926
I celebrate your faithfulness
and love for me,

01:26:05.928 --> 01:26:07.928
and I praise your name.

01:26:07.930 --> 01:26:11.365
In Thanksgiving
for this gift of my vocation,

01:26:11.367 --> 01:26:18.338
I vow to live a life of poverty,
chastity, and obedience,

01:26:18.340 --> 01:26:22.876
and to persevere
in this community until death.

01:27:07.488 --> 01:27:12.492
Lord, bless these rings
which we bless in your name.

01:27:12.494 --> 01:27:13.694
Grant that those who wear them

01:27:13.696 --> 01:27:17.364
may always have a deep faith
in each other.

01:27:17.366 --> 01:27:20.867
May they do your will
and always live together

01:27:20.869 --> 01:27:24.238
in peace, goodwill, and love.

01:27:24.240 --> 01:27:28.375
We ask this
through Christ, our lord.

01:27:30.945 --> 01:27:34.248
With this ring,

01:27:34.250 --> 01:27:37.317
I make you my wife.

01:27:37.319 --> 01:27:43.423
And with this ring,
I make you my husband.

